{"tid":1161405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國歌法委員會趕開會 毛孟靜：怕得罪西環？廖長江：遲啲答","createTime":"2019-05-19T07:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T08:28:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"041acc577a8a7ea555ad05aa144f5aab78644bf7","tid":1161405,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:21:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190519/20682183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190519%2F20682183&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=cf788cd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190519%2F20682183&h=225a34b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190519/20682183</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國歌法委員會趕開會<br />\n毛孟靜：怕得罪西環？廖長江：遲啲答<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190519/large/19la3p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F19la3p05.jpg&h=da4d0526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毛孟靜在會議上繼續狙擊廖長江「西環拆天」論。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】建制派「班長」廖長江前日在《國歌條例草案》委員會會議上意外流出「西環拆天」言論，揭露中聯辦涉嫌在背後操控立法會。民主派昨日在會議上狙擊廖長江，質問他是否怕得罪西環無好結果。廖長江亦語塞未能回應，最後只以「我遲啲答你」來逃避。<br />\n<br />\n《國歌條例草案》委員會前日開會因人數不足而點人數，委員會主席廖長江與副主席張國鈞私下交談時稱他不介意流會，但「西環實係拆天」。兩人對話被傳媒錄下播出。<br />\n相關新聞：《華爾街日報》：對港致命一擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190519/large/a0305a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190519%2Flarge%2Fa0305a.jpg&h=30169270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廖長江突然改會議時間，令部份民主派無法出席。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原定下午會議突改上午<br />\n<br />\n《國歌條例草案》委員會昨繼續開會，民主派不滿廖長江忽然將原定下午的會議改為上午，令部份人無法出席。民主派召集人毛孟靜質疑廖「趕頭趕命」開會是怕西環不高興：「我真係想問清楚，你係咪好擔心，西環你得罪佢，你真係冇好結果，你係擔心佢拆天抑或係發癲？」<br />\n<br />\n廖長江最初試圖避開不直接回應，但毛孟靜堅持不斷追問，要他解釋「點解會咁講？」廖長江即時顯得不知所措：「我只係同&hellip;&hellip;我唔會就我同&hellip;&hellip;呢個唔係規程問題，我遲啲答你。」到會議中途，毛又提出點人數：「可能流會，西環會拆天，唔該數人。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n曾稱拒西環拉票 林鄭違諾<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n吳靄儀：特首硬頸斷送港利益<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》：對港致命一擊<br />\n建測界：修例成頭上一把刀<br />\n曾稱拒西環拉票 林鄭違諾<br />\n吳靄儀：特首硬頸斷送港利益<br />\n謝偉俊撐惡法直上大會范國威反擊：徹底破壞立會監察功能"},{"pid":"919d828cea2cc9b110244113e29ecaf29b100edc","tid":1161405,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a75d1a9d28e500a1f9a0954b81c89953a1f4ec9","tid":1161405,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89376df69170b28856499b5bb51156d6a1e09924","tid":1161405,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E6%AD%8C_(1978%E5%B9%B4)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikisource.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%258E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E6%25AD%258C_%281978%25E5%25B9%25B4%29&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=5c82f746\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E6%AD%8C_(1978%E5%B9%B4)</a><br />\n<br />\n終於知道點解要禁晒 維基百科(所有語言)<br />\n原來1978年的 中共國歌<br />\n係有改到歌詞去撐 毛澤東<br />\n而&lt;義勇軍進行曲&gt; 的原作者卻被批鬥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29d0e7a24a8149d9a8870b0bf6732a00e5f9b4d","tid":1161405,"uid":206812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家曬少少時間 關心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n民陣表示，將於6月9日舉行遊行，以回應保安局局長李家超把《逃犯條例》修訂草案，直接提交大會並恢復二讀辯論。召集人岑子杰表示，目標是有30萬人參與遊行。<br />\n<br />\n民陣預計遊行在當日下午3時集合，由銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可能今次，會係最後一次<br />\n6月12如果二讀成功後，三讀應該半個月內搞掂。<br />\n為咗自己 身邊嘅屋企人 朋友 下一代<br />\n唔好再話返工不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ef3455908a8ea18c134eb489ec8689e68e4884c0","tid":1161405,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89376df69170b28856499b5bb51156d6a1e09924","tid":1161405,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E6%AD%8C_(1978%E5%B9%B4)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikisource.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%258E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E6%25AD%258C_%281978%25E5%25B9%25B4%29&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=5c82f746\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E6%AD%8C_(1978%E5%B9%B4)</a><br />\n<br />\n終於知道點解要禁晒 維基百科(所有語言)<br />\n原來1978年的 中共國歌<br />\n係有改到歌詞去撐 毛澤東<br />\n而&lt;義勇軍進行曲&gt; 的原作者卻被批鬥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"其實有需要令所有學生知道：<br />\n共産黨不想你知道既 國歌另一面歷史<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af0f38b95632134699772905eae130e4326fcbd","tid":1161405,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score